  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious muse calls upon you to investigate a Large tower in an oneiric land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first-person dungeon crawling RPG with turn-based combat and an emphasis on interacting with the characters around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Appear with no memory in a land surrounding a bizarre tower drawing in all life with a strange urge to climb it. Climb the tower to gain an understanding of why you are here, the higher you go, the more you may understand. Branching paths and dialog can lead to different outcomes or uncover new areas to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help others on their journey to climb, and have others help you. Featuring multiple endings, and paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/7b2c40110efe731e67961d69686ba2fd.poster.avif?t=1727797122\" width=88 height=30 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/7b2c40110efe731e67961d69686ba2fd.webm?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/7b2c40110efe731e67961d69686ba2fd.mp4?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/924e220766df08ae982372dc69fd6e60.poster.avif?t=1727797122\" width=88 height=30 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/924e220766df08ae982372dc69fd6e60.webm?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/924e220766df08ae982372dc69fd6e60.mp4?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/a323aa720d10b54a26bd5acd600632f3.poster.avif?t=1727797122\" width=88 height=30 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/a323aa720d10b54a26bd5acd600632f3.webm?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/a323aa720d10b54a26bd5acd600632f3.mp4?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/16a7c001d133db19158bff0ef88d2d1e.poster.avif?t=1727797122\" width=88 height=30 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/16a7c001d133db19158bff0ef88d2d1e.webm?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/16a7c001d133db19158bff0ef88d2d1e.mp4?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious muse calls upon you to investigate a Large tower in an oneiric land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first-person dungeon crawling RPG with turn-based combat and an emphasis on interacting with the characters around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Appear with no memory in a land surrounding a bizarre tower drawing in all life with a strange urge to climb it. Climb the tower to gain an understanding of why you are here, the higher you go, the more you may understand. Branching paths and dialog can lead to different outcomes or uncover new areas to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help others on their journey to climb, and have others help you. Featuring multiple endings, and paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/7b2c40110efe731e67961d69686ba2fd.poster.avif?t=1727797122\" width=88 height=30 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/7b2c40110efe731e67961d69686ba2fd.webm?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/7b2c40110efe731e67961d69686ba2fd.mp4?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/924e220766df08ae982372dc69fd6e60.poster.avif?t=1727797122\" width=88 height=30 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490060/extras/924e220766df08ae982372dc69fd6e60.webm?t=1727797122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_